{"tid":1403500,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要] 警犬最怕，一定係精液，癡粒粒","createTime":"2019-08-03T19:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T20:02:12.000Z","uid":254192,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"694304c7ae0811490b1f4049835fe80c998c9f35","tid":1403500,"uid":254192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:21:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔準打飛機 養足精神！！<br />\n用蛋液代替<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（轉發）全副武裝的抗暴警察，在獨裁國家是許多示威遊行者的惡夢，面對這樣的武裝，遊行示威的一方似乎是雞蛋碰石頭，但比起丟石頭，丟雞蛋似乎是更有效的武器。雞蛋破裂後的蛋汁會黏附在頭盔及透明盾牌上，更會對防護眼鏡帶來一陣模糊。若再加上水球，這種抗議方式往往會更加有力。在抗議現場，這種蛋洗戰術，能夠有效的減緩武裝警察的攻勢，畢竟看不清楚，就很難正確的推進及抓補，就算抗議者被抓，雞蛋跟水球很難說的上是致命武器。而且價格低廉，隨處可買，補充迅速。<br />\n<br />\n而且雞蛋跟水，雖然對人不具殺傷力，但對這些抗暴裝備，卻是十分的難以維護，溫度會讓濕掉的設備發黴，雞蛋腐壞的氣味會讓配戴者難以接受。而要清潔，需要大量的人力去清洗，抗議就是這麼回事，增加對方的成本，維持自己抗議的能量，不讓對方贏。<br />\n<br />\n網友加碼：在雞蛋面前，架設在路口的監視器也是難逃一劫。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CPsBNkw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCPsBNkw.png&h=39511a54&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d40c707dd3abe8938343a72e69c38a127cd4779","tid":1403500,"uid":110332,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:25:07.000Z","msg":"掉面，唔好掉盾"},{"pid":"5ad2ce39077f6b923854901448e5d2abbf3943ba","tid":1403500,"uid":254192,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:27:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">磚頭雜物冇用<br />\n犬隻training包 耐痛 耐攰 耐流汗 <br />\n黏性嘅嘢 定中會黐住 命中率高啲<br />\n又癡粒粒又臭<br />\n心理質素就唔係人人都有</span>"},{"pid":"271e600c2f740fd8808a80e4bcc7ec04e0fa1b87","tid":1403500,"uid":254192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:27:48.000Z","msg":"精液"},{"pid":"468940d52d882bc6719f9adbdd2aaeb518e73310","tid":1403500,"uid":254192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:27:59.000Z","msg":"精液"},{"pid":"efcee519b686466651d6c4aa3d86dc04304f7c55","tid":1403500,"uid":254192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:29:20.000Z","msg":"蛋液啊屌你"},{"pid":"68a0d1df3f9954b545438d47f31ffce01e25b6eb","tid":1403500,"uid":254192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:29:51.000Z","msg":"雞蛋撞高牆<br />\n撞佢老母"},{"pid":"9b90111bd4bac62035cfa8dcc6a2d25c3b8785c2","tid":1403500,"uid":263141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5ad2ce39077f6b923854901448e5d2abbf3943ba","tid":1403500,"uid":254192,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:27:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">磚頭雜物冇用<br />\n犬隻training包 耐痛 耐攰 耐流汗 <br />\n黏性嘅嘢 定中會黐住 命中率高啲<br />\n又癡粒粒又臭<br />\n心理質素就唔係人人都有</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:30:40.000Z","msg":"我諗起臭丸"},{"pid":"045be70852032f6e7d5d8568df91f92b8a0f2f0f","tid":1403500,"uid":254192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:31:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"56215f369fe36fb21eaa9618867d8d8148e3fa76","tid":1403500,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:31:17.000Z","msg":"大家寫左感謝信比警狗叔叔同佢啲鄰居未呀&lt;3？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1392314\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1392314</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fb0424048c0d3a1e153ba04cebbdc2798eb85e24","tid":1403500,"uid":254192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:32:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好多時係大家唔敢做一樣新嘢<br />\n係時候試新野<br />\nbe water <br />\n就地取材都係武器</span>"},{"pid":"3a5a851a4fa881003d88b216443970ef4901d639","tid":1403500,"uid":254523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T19:33:31.000Z","msg":"下次一車車雞蛋咁過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59f5580204cc3ab98038dba5203292f8e6f78b98","tid":1403500,"uid":254192,"like":0,"dislike